sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_080_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Secure Firmware Update
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisites: Firmware Management profile + security profile

    CS->>CP: 1. SignedUpdateFirmware.req
    Note right of CS: firmware.location = <Download URL><br/>firmware.signature = <signature><br/>firmware.signingCertificate = <cert>

    CP-->>CS: 2. SignedUpdateFirmware.conf

    CP->>CS: 3. SignedFirmwareStatusNotification.req
    Note left of CP: status = Downloading
    CS-->>CP: 4. SignedFirmwareStatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP: Charge Point finishes downloading

    CP->>CS: 5. SignedFirmwareStatusNotification.req
    Note left of CP: status = Downloaded
    CS-->>CP: 6. SignedFirmwareStatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP: Charge Point verifies signature

    CP->>CS: 7. SignedFirmwareStatusNotification.req
    Note left of CP: status = SignatureVerified
    CS-->>CP: 8. SignedFirmwareStatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP: Before installing: Charge Point MAY set all connectors to Unavailable

    CP->>CS: StatusNotification.req (after step 2, before step 9)
    Note left of CP: status = Unavailable
    CS-->>CP: StatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP: Charge Point starts installing firmware

    CP->>CS: 9. SignedFirmwareStatusNotification.req
    Note left of CP: status = Installing
    CS-->>CP: 10. SignedFirmwareStatusNotification.conf

    CP->>CS: 11. SignedFirmwareStatusNotification.req
    Note left of CP: status = InstallRebooting
    CS-->>CP: 12. SignedFirmwareStatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP,CS: Step 13 / 15 / 17 / 19 may arrive in different order

    CP->>CS: 13. BootNotification.req
    CS-->>CP: 14. BootNotification.conf

    CP->>CS: 15. SecurityEventNotification.req
    Note left of CP: type = FirmwareUpdated
    CS-->>CP: 16. SecurityEventNotification.conf

    CP->>CS: 17. StatusNotification.req
    Note left of CP: status = Available
    CS-->>CP: 18. StatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP: Charge Point finishes installing firmware

    CP->>CS: 19. SignedFirmwareStatusNotification.req
    Note left of CP: status = Installed
    CS-->>CP: 20. SignedFirmwareStatusNotification.conf
